com.pushtechnology.diffusion.transform.updater

Interface BoundUpdaterBuilder<S,T,U extends TransformedUpdater<S,T>,V extends TransformedUpdateSource<S,T,U>>

  • Type Parameters:
    S - The type of value understood by the topic
    T - The type of value updates are provided as
    U - The type of updater
    V - The type of update source
    All Superinterfaces:
    UpdaterBuilder<S,T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BoundSafeUpdaterBuilder<S,T>, BoundTransformedUpdaterBuilder<S,T>

    public interface BoundUpdaterBuilder<S,T,U extends TransformedUpdater<S,T>,V extends TransformedUpdateSource<S,T,U>>
extends UpdaterBuilder<S,T>
    An extension to UpdaterBuilder that is bound to a session.
    Author:
    Push Technology Limited
